3.title: Bee, Hedgehog and Ghost
3.plot: Story 83 - Bee, Hedgehog and Ghost Zack, Lily and Rex are putting on a play in costumes for the rest of Zerby Town. But during the show, Zack's costume doesn't work like they rehearsed. They'll need to keep the show going by learning to improvise. Story 114 - Pinecone Peak Rex's collection of pinecones is big enough to climb. If only Zack and Rex can figure out a way to get the pinecones to stay in a pile and not come apart when they try to climb up. Story 96 - Hole Lotta Diggin' Dotty, Zack and Sandy attempt to fill a mysterious hole in the middle of the runway at ...

4.title: Hide and Go Dotty
4.plot: Story 102 - Zerbapartments Srut and Rex have a new construction project - Zerbapartments. They're made by stacking four Zerby garages on top of each other. The Zerbies think it's great, until they realize there isn't a way to get down. Story 92 - Hide and Go Dotty Dotty the Drone has never played Hide and Seek. Zack is happy to teach her. But it turns out playing with a flying Zerby means you have to have special rules. Story 100 - Zerby Town Parade The Zerby trucks, racers and construction vehicles are all parading through Zerby Town. But each kind of vehicle wants ...

5.title: Washed Away
5.plot: Story 98 - Washed Away Walter's wash station is on top of a hill. Which means all the water from the Zerby Wash runs down the hill and causes a lot of erosion. Walter, Fill and Zack try to figure out how to get the water to flow without washing the hill away. Story 115 - Flynn Beneath My Wings Zack needs to get himself and his broken tire back to Zerby Town. But the only one around to help him is Flynn the Plane. Story 85 - More Volume Rex has created a hole right in the middle of the trail. Zack thinks they should fill it before Zerbies fall in. They set off to find ...

6.title: Chase Comes Unglued
6.plot: Story 105 - Chase Comes Unglued Logline: Chase is getting a new decal. But Mika tells him he can't fly for a full hour while the glue dries. Chase realized NOT flying is harder than he thought it would be. Story 87 - Zerby Bridges Falling Down Strut has created a new, long bridge. But it sags quite a bit in the middle. Zack and Strut know they can solve this problem. But with what? Story 90 - You've Got Some 'Splaining To Do Zack wants to build an obstacle course. He can see it perfectly in his head. Unfortunately, he isn't doing a great job explaining what he wants ...

7.title: Turn, Turn, Turn
7.plot: Story 89 - Turn, Turn, Turn Axle's new racecourse has Zack stumped. It's just a bunch of turns, but no matter what he does he can't do it without flying off the course. Lily and Axle help him figure out what's going wrong. Story 81 - A Bundle of Trouble Lily and Zack try to bring a big bundle of sticks back to the Construction Zerbies. But carrying that many sticks all at once turns out to be harder than expected. Story 88 - Fill's Big Scoop It takes ten scoops of dirt to fill Rex's bucket. That takes a long time. Fill decides having a scoop big enough to hold ten ...

8.title: Let's Get Swinging
8.plot: Story 112 - Let's Get Swinging Logline: Axle gets stuck in a gully. Zack and Rex know they can figure out a way to get him out. But they'll have to try, try again a few times to get it right. Story 93 - Gone With the Windsock Zerby Town Airport has a new windsock. Strut, Dotty and Zack try to find the best place at the airport to put it so it blows in the wind and doesn't fall over. Story 91 - Turbo, Set, Ready Lily and Zack find a path that has many natural obstacles. They decide to race the whole thing backwards. But they need to come up with a trick to remember all...

9.title: Get Back on Track Zack
9.plot: Story 110 - Get Back on Track Zack Zack needs to find Rex and tell him something. But he keeps getting distracted along the way. Zack learns the value of focusing and not getting dis- hey, a bird. Story 108 - Zerby Pirates Lily, Rose and Goldie discover a treasure map. They dress up as pirates and follow the clues on the map, hoping to find the buried treasure. Story 111 - This Way or Zack Way Zack agrees to put up signs to mark the detour around a construction site. But communicating with signs proves to be a little harder than Zack thought.

10.title: Zerby Fountain
10.plot: Story 106 - Zerby Fountain Mika has created a new fountain in the middle of Zerby Town. She wants it to be for quiet time, so Zerbies can watch the water and relax. But Zerbies would rather play in the water. Mika and Rex try to keep the Zerbies out of the water. Story 95 - Getting Nowhere Fast Axle's going full speed and he can't stop. Zack and Mika chase him around Zerby Town trying to come up with ways to slow him down long enough so Mika can see what's wrong with him and fix him. Story 84 - Sticking To It Lily and Zack are eager to help Strut and Mika finish a ...

11.title: A Funny Thing Happened
11.plot: Story 80 - A Funny Thing Happened Zack finds Lily and Axle covered in mud and each missing a tire. There's definitely a story behind what happened, if only Lily and Axle can get it in the right order - Story 104 - Think, Think Again Strut has constructed a tower out of sticks. Zack and Lily agree to help him move it, but if they make a mistake it will fall and break. Usually Zerbies try the first idea and just try, try again if it doesn't work. But this time they have to get it right on the first try. Story 103 - Flynn's Road Flynn is a float plane. He has floats. But...

1.title: The Big Move
1.plot: On a rainy day in Zerby Town Zack and Lily find a stream washing the roads away. When they get to the top of the hill and find where the stream is coming from, Zack, Lily and the Construction Zerbies try to stop it with a dam. But when it overflows the Zerbies have to put their hoods together to come up with another solution, fast!

2.title: The Zerby Town Dam
2.plot: Zack and Rex are playing in the Zerby Town sand pit when they discover a big log. They call Strut the crane to help them build a ramp out of sand so they can get on top of it. But the sand just falls apart. So Zack and Rex look for answers to make the perfect ramp up to the log. Chase the helicopter is always watching over the Zerbies, but he's having a very busy day trying to keep track of everyone. Zack offers to help Chase with his duties, but it turns out, seeing from high up like Chase can is something Zack just isn�۪t able to do. Fortunately, Lily ...

3.title: A Better Bridge
3.plot: Zack and Rex really want to play in the Zerby Town sand pit but it is too small for them both to fit. They decide to go down the forest trails sand pit and to get more sand to make it bigger. After Rex dumps the first load, they realize it will take forever. Zack offers to help but is only a little truck. Nevertheless Zack and Rex try, try again to fill the pit. Zack finds Lily in the middle of the trail, trying to keep Zerbies from running over a flower. They try to think of ways to protect the flower, while still keeping the trail open.
